🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure to accept a number and check the number is Positive and Negative or Zero.


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE check_number(n INT)
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
BEGIN
    IF n > 0 THEN
        RAISE NOTICE 'Positive Number';
    ELSIF n < 0 THEN
        RAISE NOTICE 'Negative Number';
    ELSE
        RAISE NOTICE 'Zero';
    END IF;
END;
$$;


